        <item>
            <title>Silent Hill 2 Remake 获压倒性好评，高度还原原作恐怖氛围</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/09/silent-hill-2-remake/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=silent-hill-2-remake</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/09/silent-hill-2-remake/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:24:27 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[silent hill]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Silent Hill 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Silent Hill 2 Remake]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1267855</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Silent Hill 2 重制版近日正式登陆 PS5、Steam 并开放游玩，吸引大批玩家下载游玩，并取得压倒性好评。玩家对游戏画质提升和故事氛围的重塑表示高度肯定，这款经典游戏重制版无论音效还是画面的表现均让玩家表示可重新体验原作中的紧张与恐惧。开发商表示期望通过持续更新让游戏达到玩家期望。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1267929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/462232690_1070594244-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/462232690_1070594244-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/462232690_1070594244.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/462232690_1070594244-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1070594208324868">SikthyGames@Facebook</a></p><p>玩家普遍认为 Silent Hill 2 Remake 可高度还原原作恐怖的氛围，配合画面技术大幅跃升，令整体恐怖感觉更上一层楼。然而部分玩家指游戏的操作方式与现代标准相比略嫌过时，特别是对新玩家来说，这可能会影响整体游戏体验。即使如此，这些批评未能削弱玩家对游戏的整体好评，显示经典恐怖游戏在当今仍具有强大的吸引力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268016" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241008192135-694x358.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241008192135-694x358.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241008192135.jpg 1236w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲截至香港时间今日 7 时半游戏获 4,705 个评论，当中有 96% 给予好评<br />
图片来源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2124490/SILENT_HILL_2/">Steam</a></p><p>有玩家在 Reddit 分享了第一天的游玩感受。认为重制版在保留原作精髓的同时，对场景细节和音效设计的优化做得相当出色，让玩家感受到更真实、更恐怖的游戏体验。虽然也有部分玩家提到游戏的操控感需要进一步改善，尤其是在角色移动和战斗操作上，但整体而言，玩家的评价仍然十分积极。</p><p>先前 Silent Hill 2 Remake 女主角外观惹起争议，以及游戏角色服装转变令玩家批评开发者「根本不理解衣服在原作的意义」，因此在发售前曾引起部分忠实玩家抵制。及后开发团队将事件变成游戏内容，Silent Hill 2 Remake 中 Maria 会在特定场景手持原作服饰问玩家：「喂，你觉得我穿这件好看吗？（Hey. You Think I&#8217;d look good in this one?）」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268017" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gy7nrkuxoaawkw21-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gy7nrkuxoaawkw21-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gy7nrkuxoaawkw21.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-media-max-width="560"><p dir="ltr" lang="zxx">. <a href="https://t.co/kCXROc9bji">pic.twitter.com/kCXROc9bji</a></p><p>— Demolicious (@Demolition_d) <a href="https://twitter.com/Demolition_d/status/1841635070961930627?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">October 3, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br />
资料来源：<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2124490/SILENT_HILL_2/">Steam</a>、<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/PS5/comments/1fy6pfi/silent_hill_2_remake_day_one_impressions_from_an/">Reddit</a>、<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%8A%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%982%E3%80%8B%E9%87%8D%E8%A3%BD%E7%89%88steam%E7%8D%B2%E5%BE%97%E5%A3%93%E5%80%92%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%BD%E8%A9%95%E6%88%90%E7%B8%BE%EF%BC%81%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%95%86%E6%89%9B%E4%BD%8F%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-040915172.html">Yahoo</a>、<a href="https://x.com/Demolition_d/status/1841635070961930627">Demolition_d@X</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/09/silent-hill-2-remake/game-channel/">Silent Hill 2 Remake 获压倒性好评，高度还原原作恐怖氛围</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/09/silent-hill-2-remake/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
